title: The Unseelie Court
description: The Seelie and Unseelie Courts are at war.On one side: Noble knights, fighting for freedom. On the other: Not-so-noble terrorists, fighting for the right to rule.Caught in the middle: A very confused, very lost teenage boy from Indiana.His name is Frotwoot Crossley. And he's about to find out that, somehow, that's not even the weirdest thing about him...
author: Charlie    Ward
